# packets capture tool

tcpdump -i eth0 -c 1000 -XX -w ~/captured.pcap

# -i: to specific a network card
# -c: to define how many packets to capture
# -XX: to capture the packets both in HEX and ASCII format
# -w: to save the inforamtion of captured packets into a file (@.pcap@ is for comptability of CocoaPacketAnalyzer)
